        <head xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c7-Hd1e3741">I, P. 1, Inq. 1, Tract. 6, Q. 6, C. 7</head>
        <head xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c7-Hd1e3744" type="question-title">UTRUM MERITORIUM SIT DOLERE DE PASSIONIBUS SANCTORUM<!--9-->.</head>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c7-d1e3747">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Item, quaeritur utrum meritorium sit dolere de
          <lb ed="#Q"/>passionibus sanctorum vel velle illas.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c7-d1e3754">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>a. Quia pium est lugere Martinum et pium est<!--p-->
          <lb ed="#Q"/>gaudere de<!--q--> Martino<!--10-->; ergo est meritorium
          <lb ed="#Q"/>nolle<!--r--> mortem Martini<!--11-->.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c7-d1e3763">
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Contra: 1. Hoc erat contrarium voluntati divi<lb ed="#Q"/>nae,
          et hoc sciebant<!--12-->.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="ahsh-l1p1i1t6q6c7-d1e3771">
          <cb ed="#Q" n="b"/>
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Respondeo: Velle contrarium divinae voluntati
          <lb ed="#Q"/>dicitur dupliciter: velle contrarium eius quod scio
          <lb ed="#Q"/>Deum<!--s--> velle, et hoc potest esse<!--t--> meritorium;
          <lb ed="#Q"/>vel volendo contrarium eius quod scio Deum me<!--u-->
          <lb ed="#Q"/>velle, et hoc non potest esse meritorium. â€” Vel
          <lb ed="#Q"/>aliter: de praesentibus passionibus sanctorum
          <lb ed="#Q"/>debemus dolere, de praeteritis vero possumus
          <lb ed="#Q"/>gaudere.
        </p>
      </div>
